{"tid":1499391,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"政府轉新風 白色恐怖打散和理非","createTime":"2019-08-23T16:41:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T03:09:52.000Z","uid":94771,"like":71,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"ae9177a193cb7d129983397c30417b90ebd55dcb","tid":1499391,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:41:09.000Z","msg":"睇完依個星期的白色恐怖<br />\n白色恐怖會嚴重破壞同路人團結<br />\n好明顯依家政府想打壓和理非 之後孤立勇武<br />\n<br />\n所以運動當務之急 一定要打散白色恐怖<br />\n如果唔係和理非會連遊行都唔敢去<br />\n<br />\n所以星期一國秦 一定要幫拖<br />\n同玩白色恐怖的人講 你玩白色恐怖就同你攬炒 日日搞9佢<br />\n<br />\n不過員工就唔好屌 因為目標係高層<br />\n你屌員工就變咗本未倒置<br />\n<br />\n歡迎討論<br />\n<br />\n一定要打破白色恐怖  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n和理非散咗唔怕啦 唔理了  <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a775d4f2056c07ac96a08681dfef9ac3d34d6f67","tid":1499391,"uid":242724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:45:02.000Z","msg":"PUSH"},{"pid":"32f7567e77c1f8dc8db675917c50b392245c5745","tid":1499391,"uid":114802,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:49:35.000Z","msg":"唔好意思，借個位宣傳<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong>五大訴求，缺一不可</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\">獨立調查 撒回惡法 平反暴動 撒銷檢控</span><span style=\"font-size: large;\"> <strong><span style=\"color: red;\">雙真普選</span></strong></span><br />\n<strong>堅拒階段性勝利！</strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">全民文宣鍵戰</span></span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />各區連儂牆、airdrop、派街招、擺街站、facebook &amp; instagram瘋狂轉貼文宣<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每人一個twitter account，like &amp; retweet 有關反送中的消息<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />全面推廣中共納粹主義，增加國際迴響 <span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>#ChiNazism</strong></span>，谷行全球抗共<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">文宣source:</span> <br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkposter777\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkposter777&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6n6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=852e212c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkposter777</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6n6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=4618fb14\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo</a><br />\n[國際版] <a href=\"https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo_int\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fhkstandstrong_promo_int&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6n6wbxYc%2FTJ4q%2BCB20867y4%3D&h=a072b474\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/hkstandstrong_promo_int</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: green;\">重要！重設tg account！</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">所有用自己電話號碼註冊嘅tg全部同我delete acount</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n點set private都會有可能見到你號碼！！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同我幫買張太空卡註冊個新嘅account，唔好懶！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n重設後跟以下link<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">記得做以下步驟 ，保私隱平安，「Telegram 預設唔安全」</span><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497159\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497159</a>"},{"pid":"79e0f6554242b73cddff5f679da33a6afa2ee665","tid":1499391,"uid":216789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:49:36.000Z","msg":"<strong>慎防黑惡勢力蔓延禍港，提防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團</strong><br />\n<br />\n鑒於近日有無辜香港市民慘遭黑勢力人仕襲擊，現懇切呼籲各香港市民不論男女，請慎防本地非法操縱妓女賣淫集團，保障自身安全，萬事小心，<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">切忌助長黑惡勢力氣焰</span></strong>"},{"pid":"e0582e7d477251c96ade9bf24ea11daa37a9e526","tid":1499391,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:56:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33316d9e599b5bd55baec5bb0699a894c3411ee6","tid":1499391,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:56:15.000Z","msg":"打倒白色恐怖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fe3e727527d4f6c5d1db787b2acf878712cedb42","tid":1499391,"uid":235025,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T16:59:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"04a04ec59b3090c28f18f75154cc4d77cf0a363a","tid":1499391,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:23:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"719177d4f06c8b57d0c65fc189ca391f257bdff4","tid":1499391,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:24:53.000Z","msg":"香港人無路可退<br />\n香港人一定要團結"},{"pid":"6329ff1177d5ac58df86b77e95a70a47e7a6e82a","tid":1499391,"uid":14494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T17:26:17.000Z","msg":"經過今晚, 結論係打唔散"},{"pid":"c671909a37ac362229b9e1c7a1aa323229f86d79","tid":1499391,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T00:32:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" c